	<li class="comment-li">
		<article id="comment-339586" class="comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1 comdiv">
			<div class="commeta">
				<ul>
					<li class="comauth">SUBBU</li>
					<li class="comdate"><time datetime="2017-11-18T07:05:24+01:00">November 18, 2017 7:05am</time></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
						<div class="comright">
				<div class="comcontent notop nobot">
										<p>The use of Pumpkin as a dessert is also very popular in India eg Pumpkin halwa which is a sweet made with grated pumpkins,sugar and  cardomom spice.This is something to die for</p>
				</div>
				<div class="comactions">
					<ul>
