				</div>
			</div>
		</article>
</li><!-- #comment-## -->
	<li class="comment-li">
		<article id="comment-339603" class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1 comdiv">
			<div class="commeta">
				<ul>
					<li class="comauth">Melissa</li>
					<li class="comdate"><time datetime="2017-11-18T23:40:25+01:00">November 18, 2017 11:40pm</time></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
						<div class="comright">
				<div class="comcontent notop nobot">
										<p>This is cooling as I write and I’m Wonder if it’s possible to freeze the backed cake? Is there anything special to freezing a while cheesecake? Thanks!</p>
				</div>
				<div class="comactions">
					<ul>
